---
title: Spiced Organic Beef Patties with Tomato Pan Sauce plus Rainbow Vegetable Jumble
description: If you love meatballs and you love burgers, you’re going to go batty for these patties! First you’ll form pork meatballs with minced onion and our Tunisian-inspired blend of smoky-savory spices. Then, you’ll smash the meatballs into juicy patties right in the pan to create extra-crispy edges. Meanwhile a colorful combo of carrot, zucchini, and red onion are roasting in the oven. That’s yummy enough, it’s true, but we wouldn’t leave you high and dry—you’ll make a quick tomato-y pan sauce to top it all off!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6436fbfc3897f65c4d0d7fc4-8c83c60a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/spiced-organic-beef-patties-with-tomato-pan-sauce-6436fbfc3897f65c4d0d7fc4-2ac29568.pdf
cuisine: Mediterranean
servings: 2
time required: 35 minutes
